instruction: Describe the visualization of a flock of birds migrating.
output: The sky was a tapestry of feathery forms, stretched out in a never-ending wave of movement. Thousands of birds flew in graceful arcs, slanting and gracefully looping around one another in a mesmerising spectacle. As each flock flew, they left behind a mesmerizing rainbow of hues, their feathers catching and reflecting the light of the sun.
